          "order": 1,
          "title": "DUNESQL OFFICIALLY LAUNCHED",
          "summary": "Dune has officially launched DuneSQL, aimed at creating the fastest and most convenient crypto data querying experience. DuneSQL, based on the open-source query engine Trino, will eventually replace Spark SQL and Postgres. DuneSQL provides blockchain-specific enhancements, and its roadmap includes materialized views, user-defined functions, querying personal data sources, and more. To help users migrate to DuneSQL, an automated tool has been created that will prompt users to move queries from Dune Engine V2.",
